<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="613">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="613">Occurs on the Atlantic coast from central Veracruz to central Panama, and on the Pacific coast from Costa Rica to central Panama.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
